Meredith Salenger https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meredith_Salenger 0 Meredith Dawn Salenger (born March 14, 1970) is an American actress. She is best known for her title role in the 1985 film The Journey of Natty Gann and the 1989 teen comedy, Dream a Little Dream.
